Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.62,0:00:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有证人在场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.59,0:00:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是... 不认识的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.05,0:00:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都说到这种地步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是真的不在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.02,0:00:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 这张卡片放在了比我原来埋得更深的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.18,0:00:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都觉得很不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.93,0:00:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学为什么要选她做妹妹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.76,0:00:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样没什么特点的平凡学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.62,0:00:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她与祥子同学一点也不相衬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.36,0:01:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.92,0:01:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿越与身同高的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.39,0:01:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.01,0:01:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让裙子的摺痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.83,0:01:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让白色的水手服领结外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.01,0:01:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒缓的行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.93,0:01:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.36,0:03:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}红色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早醒来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.48,0:03:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先浮现在脑中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.33,0:03:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是“今天是情人节”这个事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.54,0:03:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 鹈泽美冬从高中开始进入了莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.26,0:03:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 与其它的外部应试者稍微有点不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.02,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 我曾在莉莉安的幼儿园上过一阵学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.60,0:03:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起 祥子同学对我来说就已经是一种特殊的存在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安 美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安 友子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.41,0:03:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.62,0:04:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学拥有着与他人不同的某种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.59,0:04:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可说是天生而来的 某种令人难以接近的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.02,0:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是绘画 还是跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学都不会输给任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳得真好 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.98,0:04:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使受到夸奖 她也并未与其它人变得更亲近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.71,0:04:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓小孩子 就是会对拥有与自已不同气质的人而感到敏感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于同班同学所投射过来的惊奇的目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.97,0:04:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学毫不在意地只以沉郁的表情无视掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学在无言地战斗着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.20,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为同班同学某句无心的话 她开始换乘班车来上学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.68,0:05:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是让车送到离自已家最近的候车点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再从那里乘上班车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了这种费劲的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而平凡的我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.67,0:05:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不可遏制地追寻着\N那样的祥子同学在平常的点点滴滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.70,0:05:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那份幸福并未持续多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父亲的调职决定后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也即将离开莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就不能再看到祥子同学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.61,0:05:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我 也并非是觉得与祥子同学分别很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.63,0:05:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因无法再看到祥子同学\n而感觉到深深的遗憾而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.94,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～ 是血 不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快叫老师来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.17,0:06:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在干什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为不听老师的嘱咐才会受到惩罚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.24,0:06:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了在从秋千上跌下来前\N所看到的祥子同学那不愉快的表情的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为站着荡秋千是被规章所禁止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给你了 我另外多带了一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与祥子同学的对话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从别人那里得到什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.53,0:07:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久 到了我离开幼儿园的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了送给你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 妈妈叫我要送还给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.87,0:07:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说这是谢礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.86,0:07:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请替我向美冬的妈妈说声谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.66,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次从祥子同学\n的嘴里听到自已名字的瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.22,0:07:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是永别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再回到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会再回到她的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.58,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年后 我回到了莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大后的祥子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.84,0:08:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是如同圣母玛莉亚一般优雅而恬静的女性吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.17,0:08:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我急切地期盼着再会的那一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.59,0:08:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在哪里见过吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学 老师在叫你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能暂时失陪一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.09,0:08:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.92,0:08:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一刻 我充份地明白了人不是那么容易改变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.97,0:08:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她仍旧是全身洋盈着让他人无法接近的威严感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样毫无特点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连印象也没法让她留下的平凡的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与她之间的距离感与十年前完全没有变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.60,0:09:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是众多的同班同学中的一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.08,0:09:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久 她成了红蔷薇的花蕾的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了离我更远的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.18,0:09:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 我也因回到了\N能注视着祥子同学的生活而感到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年能交给她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概还是交不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为去年的情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁的巧克力也没有接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.52,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 我不能接受这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没有接受的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有接受的理由也许就能让她接受了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那时一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了今天的寻宝活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要去将卡片藏在某处！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我压抑不住自已的好奇心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.13,0:11:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 祥子同学的红色卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.29,0:11:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花蕾们到底把卡片藏在哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是蔷薇馆最可疑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.51,0:11:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会找到祥子同学的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的卡片就像是一张王牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.37,0:11:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要怎么使用全看我的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.07,0:11:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是今天的值日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.77,0:11:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大森老师不是说过\N“立刻来理科准备室取第五节课要用的资料”吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美冬同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮忙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一点儿资料我一个人就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.81,0:12:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.88,0:12:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就拜讬你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.99,0:12:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到祥子同学的脸后 我变得害怕起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.43,0:12:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把偷偷先找到的卡片\n若无其事地拿到蔷薇馆去的胆量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.34,0:12:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在放回去的话 还来得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好不容易才到手的卡片却...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.85,0:12:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红 白 黄的卡片将分别藏在校内的某处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限制时间是一小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.56,0:12:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到卡片后 请带回到作为本部的蔷薇馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.38,0:12:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着就可获赠\N作为附加奖的与花蕾们的半天约会权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.80,0:12:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我犹豫的时候 寻宝活动开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢啊 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为想要的东西就摆在眼前 竟未做多想就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.36,0:13:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 终于理解到自已所做所为的严重性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须把它放回原来的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.47,0:13:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 即使还了回去 像这种地方一定不会有人来找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.06,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即便如此 我也没资格就这样拿着它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.25,0:13:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要祥子同学回头看看我而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.49,0:13:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为不听老师的嘱咐才会受到惩罚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是受到惩罚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.39,0:13:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与这张红色卡片一起 被关在了这个古旧的温室里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.05,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 好像吓到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.10,0:14:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是来这里找卡片吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.02,0:14:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福泽佑巳同学 是祥子同学所选的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.09,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 祥子同学将隐藏的地点告诉了佑巳同学呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话 我也能稍微安心一点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.75,0:14:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那些一无所知地寻找祥子同学卡片的人来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学跟我一样罪孽深重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.35,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是狗一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.58,0:14:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 像这样拼命地 干劲十足地掘着土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说佑巳同学...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.53,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想卡片应该就在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么认真的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.39,0:14:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学果然是靠自已的力量找到这里来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话 请用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.71,0:14:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.32,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么挖也无法在那里找到卡片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.19,0:15:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但越是把这一结局往后拖延\n我就越觉得自已变得污秽似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法再忍耐着看下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那里没有卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.10,0:15:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我说晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上我刚才也挖掘过那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会认为卡片在那里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.01,0:15:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然事前没有被告知过 那么佑巳同学是怎么找到这里来的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.04,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个蔷薇就叫做红蔷薇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是红蔷薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同祥子同学的分身般的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.93,0:15:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以祥子同学才会将卡片藏在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.51,0:15:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 只有佑巳同学察觉到了这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.21,0:15:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全地输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.80,0:16:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明如此的接近 我却完全未察觉到这种花的含义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到4点40分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.18,0:16:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加活动的同学们请立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.13,0:16:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.35,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动结束了 请立刻到中庭集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.86,0:16:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直觉得很不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.84,0:16:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就在这里分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.68,0:16:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.54,0:16:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学为什么会选择她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她与祥子同学一点也不相衬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我擅自地那样认定着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但通过今天的事我明白了一些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.09,0:16:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学拥有着我所没有的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而祥子同学发现了这些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.77,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学的确有看人的眼光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到“中”的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会无一例外地获赠与我的半天约会权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.05,0:17:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 那个 这是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.97,0:17:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.89,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.79,0:17:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个... 那么这周的周日如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.77,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你想去哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去佑巳想去的地方就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让我先想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会期待着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.45,0:17:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学入学考试做得还好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 今天的估计不大好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你反倒是相当的愉快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.09,0:18:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为托了寻宝活动的福 我的愿望实现了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.42,0:18:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是那个“在毕业之前 我想看看蔷薇馆里普通学生们喧闹的样子”吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.09,0:18:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 今天是我到目前为止的人生中最好的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.84,0:18:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.45,0:18:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.75,0:18:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我能去您家里拜访您吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.47,0:18:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有东西想交给您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.71,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把卡片藏在那么奇怪的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.26,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把卡片夹在“江户的物价”什么的书间 太难明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 生气了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种话等一会儿再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我也会去由乃的家里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 姐姐 等会儿再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也是夹心巧克力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是特意送到家里来的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.23,0:19:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是惯例的手制品了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.42,0:19:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 从静那里得到了酒心巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃点暖暖身体吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.23,0:19:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐在某些地方真是有点迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.18,0:19:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.39,0:19:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.83,0:19:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让我拿了专为姐姐而做的礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静大人会是一种什么心情呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.98,0:19:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 又给我上了一堂课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.19,0:19:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得很自大的样子真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.15,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有一个懂事的妹妹我真是幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.63,0:19:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能轻松坦然地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.02,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 请不要这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.85,0:20:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果姐姐不在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了春天 志摩子也会成为二年级生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.70,0:20:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生入学后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.62,0:20:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再察觉时 我的离开也就变得很平常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不觉得会是那么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.05,0:20:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大理石花纹巧克力蛋糕 真是非常好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.69,0:20:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.18,0:21:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有关本周日的事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.68,0:21:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 能请你先回教室吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.45,0:21:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 祥子同学的缝纫箱就先放在我这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.72,0:21:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拜讬你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.11,0:21:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会先放在祥子同学的桌上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟姐姐慢慢地谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 周日的事是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.47,0:21:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没有发觉是我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.64,0:21:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 美冬同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.23,0:21:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个发型很适合你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.96,0:22:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我已能坦诚地为祥子同学\N有了一个很棒的妹妹这件事而高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.66,0:22:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是发型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.70,0:22:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我内心的深处 也正在发生细微的变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.13,0:23:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅绽放着的纯白的蔷薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.71,0:23:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那朵白色蔷薇所隐藏的过去究竟是...
